songs.title: My Heart Belongs to You
songs.lyrics:
Hey baby, you know you're my world right?
C'mon. it's you and only you. haha
Cuz my heart belongs to you baby
Oh, my heart belongs to you, di, di, di, di-ohh my love
Oh me corazon es tu yo di, di, di, di todo me amor
Having you by my side, really completes my life
Cause I don't know, what I'd do if I didn't have you-oh
Estamos mui bien-that's what I sing
Oh, my heart belongs to you, di, di, di, di-ohh my love
Oh me corazon es tu yo di, di, di, di todo me amos
Que pesa mommy, oh you look so sweet
I'm so proud to be your one and only
Me amor, for you my dear
Ain't no need for you to go nowhere
Everything you need is right here...
I'll love you for the rest of my life
And I swear I can't wait just to make you my wife
Te amo con me vita me bonita
Always be my girl, I promise I'll give you the world
Oh, my heart belongs to you, di, di, di, di-ohh my love
Oh me corazon es tu yo, di, di, di, di todo me amos
